descript.abstract: Source: https://data.calgary.ca/Demographics/Calgary-Equity-Index-Overlay-Statistics/7g5f-dkmi/about_dataCollection date: 10/16/25CRS: NAD 1983 CSRS UTM Zone 11NProcessing steps: Feature to Point tool to create centroids. Attribute definitions:ATTRIBUTE: the CEI is measures many indicators, in this case the indicator selected is median incomeVALUE: median income valueVALUE_LABEL: median income value distinguished by data type (currency)AREA_Type: type of area values is measured in; in this case it is CSA.AREA_ID: ID for area locationCEI_RANKING: quartile ranking determined by CEI for each CSA by median income.TARGET_FID: ID of the target feature from joinNEAR_FID: FID of nearest vaccination siteNEAR_DIST: nearest distance in meters
descript.purpose: The purpose of this table is show centroid location for each CSA in Calgary

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.
